  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Haveged</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Haveged</application> package contains a daemon
      that generates an unpredictable stream of random numbers
      et feeds the /dev/random device.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

